Similar in concept to the [[Baragwin/Legends|Baragwin]] [[Baragwin Shadow Armor|Stealth Armor]], '''this belt''' was a quantum leap in advancement over standard stealth units. It provided greater camouflage than a standard [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth belt]] and enhanced the mobility and situational awareness of the wearer to potential threats.

